{"id":2663,"date":"2023-09-26T10:20:20","date_gmt":"2023-09-26T03:20:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2663"},"modified":"2023-09-26T10:20:20","modified_gmt":"2023-09-26T03:20:20","slug":"khoi-dau-hanh-trinh-den-xu-so-mat-troi-moc-cung-trung-nam-sinh-vien-qtkd-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/khoi-dau-hanh-trinh-den-xu-so-mat-troi-moc-cung-trung-nam-sinh-vien-qtkd-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do\/","title":{"rendered":"KH\u1edeI \u0110\u1ea6U H\u00c0NH TR\u00ccNH \u0110\u1ebeN \u201cX\u1ee8 S\u1ede M\u1eb6T TR\u1edcI M\u1eccC\u201d C\u00d9NG TRUNG NAM &#8211; SINH VI\u00caN QTKD TR\u01af\u1edcNG \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC TH\u00c0NH \u0110\u00d4"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trung Nam &#8211; sinh vi\u00ean K12 ng\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kinh doanh kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Internship Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u sinh vi\u00ean v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t m\u1edbi, v\u0103n h\u00f3a m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u00ean c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng ty LETCO, Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Internship \u2013 th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp sinh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4. Tham gia ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh, sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 v\u0103n minh, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0m th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp sinh, sinh vi\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c thu nh\u1eadp h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn l\u00ean t\u1edbi 30.000.000\u0111\/th\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_18310\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18310\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-18310 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/MEO03134-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-18310\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Trung Nam &#8211; sinh vi\u00ean Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kinh doanh (\u1edf gi\u1eefa) ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ng\u00e0y 24\/09 v\u1eeba qua, Trung Nam &#8211; sinh vi\u00ean ng\u00e0nh QTKD \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 bay sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp 12 th\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i \u201cx\u1ee9 s\u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc\u201d. Th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp doanh nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian quan tr\u1ecdng m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 sinh vi\u00ean t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, v\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Trung Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi v\u00e0 r\u00e8n r\u0169a trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 m\u1edf mang t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng, l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n v\u0103n h\u00f3a m\u1edbi, t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/IYZNZcrdeVE?si=NZMuROskDL_dMJA2\" width=\"560\" height=\"314\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trung Nam chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m trong c\u00e1c m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c kh\u00e1c nhau s\u1ebd gi\u00fap sinh vi\u00ean s\u1edbm c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh &#8211; \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh trang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc ra tr\u01b0\u1eddng xin vi\u1ec7c, khi sinh vi\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp v\u00e0 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7n, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, trau d\u1ed3i ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_18308\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18308\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-18308 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/MEO03107-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-18308\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nh\u00e0 Tr\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eedi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u00fac \u0111\u1ebfn Trung Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u00fac Trung Nam c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n sinh vi\u00ean \u0111ang tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 tin, b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u00e0 Tr\u01b0\u1eddng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho Thadoers ph\u00e1t huy n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0i b\u00e3o. Ch\u00fac Trung Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m vui, h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u1edbi, m\u1edf mang tri th\u1ee9c, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><strong>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9: Km15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>Hotline: 0934 07 8668 \u2013 0243 386 1601<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>Website: <\/i><\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/\"><b><i>https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/<\/i><\/b><\/a><b><i>\u00a0<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>Fanpage: <\/i><\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo\"><b><i>https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo<\/i><\/b><\/a><\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trung Nam &#8211; sinh vi\u00ean K12 ng\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kinh doanh kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp doanh nghi\u1ec7p. Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Internship Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u sinh vi\u00ean v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i m\u00f4i [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":2664,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[36,1],"tags":[109,110,112,42],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2663"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-j